OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F406A1776767959
OL,3,CAntisemitic attacks on Jewish sites
OL,4,Care 'abhorrent' says security minister
OL,6,FA series of antisemitic attacks on
OL,7,FJewish sites in London are "abhorrent"
OL,8,Fand "unacceptable", security minister
OL,9,FDan Jarvis said.
OL,11,FSpeaking at Finchley Reform Synagogue,
OL,12,Fwhich was subject last week to an
OL,13,Fattempted arson attack, Mr Jarvis said
OL,14,Fthe government was working closely
OL,15,Fwith police on the investigation.
OL,26,@oD@\OUoD@fO]pD@EOUpD@RO]
