PN,40602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F406A1776767959
OL,3,CAntisemitic attacks on Jewish sites
OL,4,Care 'abhorrent' says security minister
OL,6,FHe added: "The attacks that we've seen
OL,7,Fin recent times are completely
OL,8,Fabhorrent and unacceptable, and we
OL,9,Fwill move heaven and earth to make
OL,10,Fsure that people feel properly
OL,11,Fsupported."
OL,13,FMetropolitan Police Deputy
OL,14,FCommissioner Matt Jukes said social
OL,15,Fmedia platforms should do more to
OL,16,Fprevent antisemitic posts being shared
OL,17,Fonline.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/8
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,407,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F406A1776767959
OL,3,CAntisemitic attacks on Jewish sites
OL,4,Care 'abhorrent' says security minister
OL,6,FHe joined Dan Jarvis in north London
OL,7,Fand confirmed officers had made 15
OL,8,Farrests in relation to a string of
OL,9,Fevents.
OL,11,F"There is quite an age range there, a
OL,12,Frange of backgrounds, but we do know
OL,13,Fthat, in some cases, young people have
OL,14,Fbeen drawn into online conversations,
OL,15,Fimagining there is quick or easy money
OL,16,Fto make," Mr Jukes said.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/8
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,407,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F406A1776767959
OL,3,CAntisemitic attacks on Jewish sites
OL,4,Care 'abhorrent' says security minister
OL,6,F"We will continue to work hard on the
OL,7,Fonline space. It is a job for the
OL,8,Fwider security, intelligence services
OL,9,Fand counter-terrorism policing. But
OL,10,Fit's also something we think that the
OL,11,Fplatforms could contribute more to,
OL,12,Fbecause there is online sharing and
OL,13,Fpromulgation of antisemitic conspiracy
OL,14,Ftheories.
OL,16,F"You can see those even this week,
OL,17,Fafter instances that have affected
OL,18,Fsynagogues like this one here, people
OL,19,Fhave to look at antisemitic posts
OL,20,Fabout conspiracy theories.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/8
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,407,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F406A1776767959
OL,3,CAntisemitic attacks on Jewish sites
OL,4,Care 'abhorrent' says security minister
OL,6,F"That kind of content is helping
OL,7,Fcreate an environment that some have
OL,8,Fdescribed as ambient antisemitism, but
OL,9,Fit's actually very visible
OL,10,Fantisemitism, and I believe we would
OL,11,Fask that platforms play their part in
OL,12,Faddressing that."
OL,14,FTwo teenagers have been arrested in
OL,15,Fconnection with the arson attack in
OL,16,FHarrow.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G5/8
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
