PN,40606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F406A1776767959
OL,3,CAntisemitic attacks on Jewish sites
OL,4,Care 'abhorrent' says security minister
OL,6,FA "bottle with some sort of accelerant
OL,7,Fhad been thrown through the window" at
OL,8,FKenton United Synagogue at around
OL,9,Fmidnight on Sunday, a spokesperson for
OL,10,Fthe Met police previously said.
OL,12,FThe Community Security Trust (CST)
OL,13,Fsaid that minor smoke damage to an
OL,14,Finternal room was caused but said no
OL,15,Fthere were injuries or significant
OL,16,Fstructural damage.
OL,18,FYehuda Black, the synagogue's rabbi,
OL,19,Fsaid the item was thrown into the
OL,20,Fmedical room.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G6/8
