PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F406A1776767959
OL,3,CAntisemitic attacks on Jewish sites
OL,4,Care 'abhorrent' says security minister
OL,6,FChief Rabbi Sir Ephraim Mirvis
OL,7,Fdescribed the arson attack as
OL,8,F"cowardly" and said "a sustained
OL,9,Fcampaign of violence and intimidation
OL,10,Fagainst the Jewish community of the UK
OL,11,Fis gathering momentum".
